Persistence/Entity version 0.07
===========================
    Persistence layer

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Abstract::Meta::Class 
  DBIx::Connection
  SQL::Entity
  Simple::SAX::Serializer
  Storable

